Name: INU
About the game: INU is animated licking doge screenmate application. Feature Simple sprite animation. Random-moving on screen, as top level window always. Support Windows 11 and Windows 10 (need for DirectX 12, Feature level 12_0). CommandLine Option Usage: inu.exe [quantity] [gaben] Option: quantity: Much INU (1-666). gaben: Such easter egg. INU Properties > GENERAL > LAUNCH OPTIONS How to exit Click the INU icon on taskbar-corner. If you see of the following window Unfortunately, your computer can't execute for INU application, let's uninstall and post much humorous review!
